Subject: [PATCH] mptcp: pm: avoid code duplication to lookup endp

The helper __lookup_addr() can be used in mptcp_pm_nl_get_local_id()
and mptcp_pm_nl_is_backup() to simplify the code, and avoid code
duplication.

